    "body": " `addr_from_alloc_id` takes AllocId and returns vaddr, allocating vaddr when the allocation doesn't have such vaddr.\n\nIt also records the paddr in int_to_ptr_map. The paddr is found via `mirch::page_walk_or`  or `kernel_code_vaddr_to_paddr`.\n\nWe should refactor all physical addresses saved in state by making them virtual addresses, because each vaddr must correspond to a paddr through page table, whereas a paddr can be shared in multiple vaddr. `alloc_id_from_addr` also needs the fix because it currently takes paddr, while  vaddr should be taken.\n\nPaddr is linear mapped to vaddr  in kernel code, but not in free pages due to virtual mapping.\n\n\n```\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff8001000c (alloc82) 👈 kernel static section\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010018 (alloc83)\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010028 (alloc84)\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010040 (alloc85)\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010058 (alloc5)\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010078 (alloc2)\n[page_walk] vaddr=0xffffffff80ffff4b 👈 kernel stack section\n    current_level=4 pte_paddr=0x1208ff8 mem_addr=0x736765007ff8\n    current_paddr=0x20f8000 page_table_entry=0x20f8007\n    current_level=3 pte_paddr=0x20f8ff0 mem_addr=0x736765ef7ff0\n    current_paddr=0x20fd000 page_table_entry=0x20fd007\n    current_level=2 pte_paddr=0x20fd038 mem_addr=0x736765efc038\n    current_paddr=0xe00000 page_table_entry=0xe00183\n    page_offset=0x1fff4b paddr=0xffff4b\n```\n\n<details><summary>addr_from_alloc_id (AllocId -> Vaddr)  / ptr_get_alloc (Vaddr -> AllocId)</summary>\n<p>\n\n```\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff8001000c (alloc82)\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff8001000c\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010018 (alloc83)\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010018\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010018\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010018\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010028 (alloc84)\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010028\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010028\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010028\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010028\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010040 (alloc85)\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010040\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010040\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010040\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010018\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010058 (alloc5)\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010058\n[addr_from_alloc_id - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010078 (alloc2)\n[ptr_get_alloc - page_walk_or] vaddr=0xffffffff80010078\n```\n\n</p>\n</details> ",
